$288
Burmese is one of the languages included in XLM-Rﻗs cleaned CommonCrawl training corpus. The paper says using one CommonCrawl dump for English and twelve dumps for all other languages significantly increases dataset sizes, especially for low-resource languages like Burmese and Swahili.
