$390
Japanese technical term is a source-side technical term automatically extracted from Japanese patent sentences. Japanese technical terms are aligned to Chinese translations using an SMT phrase translation table and, if needed, SMT word alignment. In training and decoding, they are replaced with technical term tokens TT_i; in the test set, 2,244 occurrences were identified in 1,857 types.
